Program: The Documentary
Title: The People's Games: London 2012
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/p00x8gpc
Last Broadcast Date: Sun 12 Aug 2012
The world's biggest sporting event is coming to an end. We capture the story of the London Olympic Games through the sounds of the people who went to, worked on and competed in them. (Image: Spectators wave union jacks and applaud during the Women's Modern Pentathlon on Day 16 of the London 2012 Olympic Games on August 12, 2012 in London, England. Photo by Alex Livesey/Getty Images) Show less